# =============================================================================
# DEPRECATED — Marketing credentials are now managed via the Admin Panel.
# =============================================================================
# All marketing API keys and credentials are stored encrypted in the
# system_credentials table and loaded by the Rust service-marketing crate
# via config_loader.rs (DB → env var fallback).
#
# To configure credentials:
#   1. Go to Admin Panel → Credentials
#   2. Add your Twitter, LinkedIn, Reddit, Dev.to, GitHub, SMTP keys
#
# The only env file needed is the root .env with infrastructure vars.
# See the root .env.example for the minimal template.
# =============================================================================
